title: Coach Expects Brees To Start Against Cowboys - Thenew995fm.com
text:
Sean Payton said after Friday's practice that he expects quarterback Drew Brees will start Sunday night against the Dallas Cowboys at the Mercedes-Benz Superdome. Brees was inactive for last Sunday's game at the Carolina Panthers with a bruised rotator cuff.
 Thenew995fm.com.
